comments: Holmgren (OKC) and Sabonis (SAC) mutually engage and disengage as marginal contact occurs off-ball.
Sabonis (SAC) is in the lane for less than three seconds when the shot is imminent.
Williams (OKC) moves alongside Monk's (SAC) path and marginal body contact occurs during his driving shot attempt. Williams reaches for the ball and avoids making contact with Monk's arm.
Murray (SAC) establishes himself in Dort's (OKC) path and he absorbs the marginal contact.
Ellis (SAC) briefly places his hands against Gilgegous-Alexander (OKC) while moving alongside his path and marginal body contact occurs during his driving shot attempt.
Fox (SAC) places a collapsed forearm to Williams' (OKC) side, and marginal contact occurs as the two come together during Fox's drive.
Holmgren (OKC) contests the driving shot attempt and marginal contact occurs with Fox's (SAC) arm after the release.
Sabonis (SAC) places his hands against Holmgren (OKC) and slides his hands off in pursuit of the loose ball.
Monk (SAC) jumps along Gilgeous-Alexander's (OKC) path and marginal body contact occurs defending his driving shot attempt.
Sabonis (SAC) briefly places his hands against Holmgren's (OKC) back and marginal contact occurs during his put-back shot attempt at the rim.
Williams (OKC) establishes a legal position alongside Fox's (SAC) path and marginal body contact occurs during his driving shot attempt.
Monk (SAC) extends his leg and makes intentional foot to ball contact.
Williams (OKC) and Fox (SAC) mutually engage and disengage as marginal contact occurs during the rebound.
Giddey (OKC) places his hands against Fox's (SAC) body, in attempt of a take foul and immediately slides his hands off during his drive in transition. The contact that occurs is marginal.
Williams (OKC) commits a take foul on Fox (SAC).
Monk (SAC) jumps slightly from point A to point B and marginal body contact occurs with Gilgeous-Alexander (OKC) while contesting the driving shot attempt.
Dort (OKC) commits a take foul on Murray (SAC).
Dort (OKC) rests a hand on Fox's (SAC) right side and marginal body contact occurs as Dort deflects the inbound pass.
Dort (OKC) is the last person to touch the ball before it goes out of bounds. Possession is correctly given to SAC.
Dort (OKC) delivers contact to Murray (SAC), dislodging him from his position and causing him to step out of bounds.
